<br>
Banish = 500 mana evocation based.<br>
<br>
SOFB = 334 mana conj based.<br>
<br>
Banish is only for if you F up aggro or something, and wait til the last wave, otherwise your group may turn out to just F up every wave... and banishment has recast time.<br>
<br>
